THE GAME
--------

  'Blokator' is a Workbench game in which you 'drop' blocks of
various shapes and colours, from the top to the bottom of the game
board. The goal is to place blocks so they are located next to
blocks of the same type and/or colour. The more blocks there are,
the more points you get.

  Have fun!

